Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:40.20,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Dressed in black, with slanted hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:45.42,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,no-one knows, what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:49.96,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,(No! no no…) Stylish looks, with shaggy beard,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:54.59,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,and chicks and scotch, relieve your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:25:04.23,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Revolver Fires! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:13.53,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Trailing notes, and smoking barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:19.49,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Like a wolf in a bush of ghosts, you never care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:24.79,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Who’s gonna get close behind your back (No no no!)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:29.59,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Never feel sorry for being all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.63,0:25:34.13,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,every minutes, every seconds, every little moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:37.97,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Never be harsh, you’re so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.60,0:25:43.14,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Gently move, with bitter jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.10,0:25:47.48,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Don’t look back, the deed is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.85,0:25:51.98,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,The sun shows up, just as bright
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:26:02.04,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Revolver Fires! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:10.79,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,Trailing notes, and smoking barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:16.72,EDENG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}A man in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:40.20,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一袭黑衣 歪戴着檐帽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.12,0:24:45.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人知道 你眼中的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.46,0:24:49.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,(不! 不 不…)摩登的外貌 拉碴的胡须
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:54.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,美女和酒精 纾解你的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:25:04.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,枪声作响 弹丸疾射
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:13.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,残音悠悠 硝烟徐徐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:19.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你就像遍布幽灵的灌木丛中的一匹狼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:24.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,从不在乎谁将从你的身后靠近(不 不 不！)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.21,0:25:29.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,从不内疚于自己的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.63,0:25:34.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕每一分 每一秒 每一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.51,0:25:37.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那样温柔 从不无情冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.60,0:25:43.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你温文尔雅 开着苦涩的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.10,0:25:47.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不要回头 诸事已毕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.85,0:25:51.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,天日重显 光芒万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:26:02.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,枪声作响 弹丸疾射
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:10.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,残音悠悠 硝烟徐徐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.34,0:26:16.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}一个黑衣人
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:56.28,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:56.49,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:56.70,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:56.91,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:57.12,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:57.32,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}墓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:57.53,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}碑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:57.74,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\t(0,50,\blur0)}前
