Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统阁下 交易顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必您明天就能看到Little Comet的光芒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么呢 快点开车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了 能出示一下您的身份证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个旗子你没有看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是玛兰达共和国的特命全权大使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是国际问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 真对不起 我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 那可是外交公用车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,180,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\bord0\fs65\fad(500,300)\blur0\t(3610,3710,\blur10)}东杜拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是一条路直通宝藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「东杜拉世界著名歌手奎因·玛露塔在西杜拉被暗杀」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「东西杜拉之间的互不侵犯条约被撕毁 邦交关系紧张」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然破坏意在和平的互不侵犯条约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西杜拉可是会变成世界公敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真搞不懂他们在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本明明是一个国家 却把无辜的人牵连进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 你还在介意那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来应该能保护她的 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想死成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这城市还真不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的犯罪防范率之高可谓世界首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟东杜拉可是聚集了享誉全球的优等生们的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会有各种大使馆和资本家豪宅林立吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是盗贼圣地对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是希望他们能够手下留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有行李
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远道而来辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说这个了 那个东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是传说在中世纪坠落在东杜拉的彗星的碎片 Little Comet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1604,980)}小彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东杜拉也太没眼光了 居然放弃这样的珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就证明他们有更渴望获得的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是西杜拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们用这颗宝石换取了我国的铀浓缩设备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的用途并不难想像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我们玛兰达共和国只是站在中立的立场上出售军火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于其用途则不是我们该干涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您亲手把玩欣赏一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是输入解锁密码的打字机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 你做什么啊 我还没问到密码呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间给你喋喋不休了 准备开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作未免太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得露出过马脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只能从这走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 他们干得还真漂亮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像把我们的行动都看穿了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是普通市民的汽车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种野蛮行径我可干不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没交通工具就只能干瞪眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁邦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅 那个开枪狙击我们的家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种子弹 我见过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 在哪里见到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奎因·玛露塔那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,150,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\fs90\bord0\fad(300,500)}7天前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,70,,{\fnFZDaBiaoSong-B06\fs55\bord0\fad(300,100)\blur0\t(2940,3340,\blur10)\b0}西杜拉 国际音乐会会场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲我们开枪的就是那个枪杀了奎因·玛露塔的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能完全确定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么找到这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是优等生之城啊 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事需要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在找什么 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道是幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经听说过一个传言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个叫耶尔·奥崎的杀手会为他目标提前立一块墓碑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从不主动杀人 只接受他人的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还从来没听说过 他是个什么角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情报几乎是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟从来没人在被他盯上之后还能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道 他好像对自己的枪法非常自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会丢骰子决定用几发子弹了结目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶庙会似的兴奋 愉快的心情 胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然嘀咕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是香芹的花语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是死亡的前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说他很享受杀人的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢得了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话我可不能当作没听到啊 难道你觉得我会输？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是没人活下来么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你还带伤 太不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界第一的枪手不需要两个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是为朋友着想才劝你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞错了 我们只是生意上的搭档而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊 那就随便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能请到您这样的美女 我们深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 你真是嘴甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本俱乐部采用会员制度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来客都是温文尔雅的资本家 不必担心会有麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在表演时间到来前就请您在此等候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 都这个点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是您这样的女士该得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快把我放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想杀我吗 次元大介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁邦三世 你怎么找到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没注意到吗 供奉在你墓前的是原生香芹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还带有微弱的银莲花的香气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近没多少开着大片银莲花的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算要别人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多心 我可不是来帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁出于什么目的雇用了耶尔·奥崎想要干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然是想要夺回大使馆宝物的那群家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么没准备我的墓碑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得这事有蹊跷 所以我来确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好事了小心送命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话我原封不动地还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经荒废了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这里不像是他的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个枪械工房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别推我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边全是通讯设备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 过来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣还挺广泛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来他的手挺巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么搞的 全都是一样的西服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉达吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(932,980)}Prada
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元你也穿的同一个牌子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我穿的牌子可多了 从纪梵希到芬迪都有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1306,980)}FENDI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1090,980)}GIVENCHY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不二子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不二子 能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音…是鲁邦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被耶尔·奥崎给盯上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想到俱乐部当舞娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果好像不小心误闯了个不得了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.52,0:15:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在盘算什么 不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得那么难听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是想金盆洗手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可能是报应不爽了吧 看样子我玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你可别说这种不吉利的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说真的 鲁邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你可别来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想连累你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是被看扁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你以为我是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不行不试一下怎么知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你要试试看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要监视不二子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人我并不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在确认我布置的东西的运作情况而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么要杀次元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么理由 我只管解决目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你有点得意忘形了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个狙击手这么靠近他的目标怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人开枪能比次元更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你犯了两个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我擅长的不仅仅是狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次 在开枪速度上是你们不及我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还欠了你一笔账呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我就跟你算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用左手来比试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 随便你什么时候拔枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:44.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,.357马格努 这种大口径子弹不适合速射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 余兴节目到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元大介 下一发子弹就会要了你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形势对你不利 暂时先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 鲁邦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没想到你会在速射上输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的枪是点22口径 很小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且改造得非常轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也用那种枪就不会输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是意气用事的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不给他一发子弹我咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用骰子来决定开几枪的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能有什么个人坚持的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才管他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算甩掉他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下他应该追不上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找他一雪前耻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他一定有盲点的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁邦 他又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难缠的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他瞄准我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不穿过对面的仓库就逃不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 一冲出去就成他枪下亡魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把话说得这么简单 我可不能死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.22,0:22:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 他是没法连我们什么时候冲出去都预测到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我数到三 我们一起朝对面仓库冲过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 这不就是在搏命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的目标可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了我就变成鬼一辈子缠着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可不愿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:22:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.20,0:23:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.96,0:23:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二 三！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元 坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 次元
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲眼看着朋友被杀的感觉如何
